<template lang="pug">
    #user-module
        Loading
        v-navigation-drawer(v-model="drawer" clipped fixed app :mini-variant="mini")
            v-list(dense)
                v-list-group(prepend-icon="account_circle" value="true")
                    v-list-tile(slot="activator" active-class="blue--text text--darken-2")
                        v-list-tile-content
                            v-list-tile-title Setting

        v-toolbar(fixed clipped-left app color="blue darken-3" dark)
            v-toolbar-side-icon(@click.stop="drawer = !drawer")
            v-toolbar-title.mr-5.align-center.site-logo
                span.title
                    router-link(to="/admin")
                        v-img.logo(:src="require('../assets/images/Hiero7.png')" contain width="120" )
            Shortcut(v-show="$vuetify.breakpoint.mdAndUp")
            v-spacer 
            Notification
            //- v-btn(icon)
            //-     v-icon notifications
            v-menu(offset-y )
                template(slot="activator" slot-scope="{on}")
                    v-btn(v-on="on" flat outline v-show="$vuetify.breakpoint.mdAndUp") 
                        span.white--text() Hello, Karen
                        //- span.white--text() Hello, {{($store.state.account.account.name == undefined)? user.name: $store.state.account.account.name}}
                    v-btn(v-on="on" flat icon v-show="$vuetify.breakpoint.smAndDown") 
                        v-icon account_circle
                v-list
                    v-list-tile(to="/admin/settings")
                        v-list-tile-title
                            span Settings
        //- Snackbar
        //- v-snackbar(v-model="$store.state.global.snackbar.status" :color="$store.state.global.snackbar.color" :timeout="$store.state.global.snackbar.timeout" top ) {{$store.state.global.snackbar.text}}
        //-     v-btn(dark flat @click="$store.dispatch('global/closeSnackbar')") CLOSE

        v-content
            //- v-container(fill-height)
            router-view
</template>

<script>
import Loading from "../components/Loading";

export default {
    components: {
        Loading
    },
    data() {
        return {
            drawer: true,
            mini: false,
            menu: false,
            items: [
                { title: "Dashboard", icon: "dashboard" },
                { title: "Account", icon: "account_box" },
                { title: "Admin", icon: "gavel" }
            ],
            right: null,
            user: {
                name: "James Bond"
            },
            userName: ""
        };
    },
    methods: {},
    watch: {},
    created() {}
};
</script>

<style lang="sass" scoped>

</style>
